{"tid":975082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"樂富廣場女子殘廁內上吊亡","createTime":"2019-01-09T11:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T13:20:43.000Z","uid":41404,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"df7534b6edf4874f0e0546555c9e020d7f1c0f4d","tid":975082,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T11:08:24.000Z","msg":"黃大仙樂富廣場，下午4時許，商場保安發現一名女子於殘廁內用尼龍繩上吊，慌忙報案。消防接報到場，將女子救下，交由救護車送往廣華醫院搶救，惟抵院後不治。警方正調查原因。<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」： <a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=GVks3%2F%2FXRBcl6rEY6c16IE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=924251a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190109/59124064\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190109%2F59124064&d=GVks3%2F%2FXRBcl6rEY6c16IE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=72f6857b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190109%2F59124064&h=1a5f88ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190109/59124064</a>"},{"pid":"9c68db88a1b29115b5cd55724f9a9133b37b2972","tid":975082,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T11:13:50.000Z","msg":"人人都有人自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0001735a83fed13026f0366b80deb98448439480","tid":975082,"uid":215634,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9c68db88a1b29115b5cd55724f9a9133b37b2972","tid":975082,"uid":215634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T11:13:50.000Z","msg"